  "id": "RAW_55f25b",
  "title": "【实践】告别“提示词炼金术”，构建不过时的 AI 工程",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzE5OTE3NTEyMA==&mid=2247484839&idx=1&sn=2daf41f936564fa93c70679c0d35628e",
  "date": "2025-08-29 01:00:00",
  "author": "AI炼金术",
  "siteName": "AI炼金术",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e250ae94&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FBMIuxTte9jIOoNyOWSYBdU3ol4QlS7ZqHEs7tYTdYJlgBliaibzayheXpOfC09HBsFBfYIdWLYz8KK1xqRpMTiaIQ%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <div style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(114, 114, 114);letter-spacing: 2.5px;line-height: 2;padding: 0px 15px;box-sizing: border-box;font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;text-align: justify;\">\n   <div style=\"padding:0px 15px;letter-spacing:2px;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 27px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">来源</span></strong></span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></strong><span style=\"font-size: 12px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Source</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 0px 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 100 100 0%;border-style: solid;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 2px;border-color: rgb(242, 227, 84) rgb(242, 227, 84) rgb(242, 227, 84) rgb(160, 160, 160);padding: 8px 11px 0px;margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"text-align: justify;letter-spacing: 1px;padding: 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;box-sizing:border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">原标题: The Bitter Lesson of AI Engineering</span></strong></span></p>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;box-sizing:border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">分享者: Omar Khattab (DSPy &amp; Databricks)</span></strong></span></p>\n      <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;box-sizing:border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接:&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qdmxApz3EJI\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qdmxApz3EJI</a></span></span></strong></span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"padding:0px 15px;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">不要痴迷于调提示词，要把时间精力投资在更稳定有复利的事儿上。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"padding:0px 15px;letter-spacing:2px;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 27px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">要点</span></b></span><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></b><span style=\"font-size: 12px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Key Takeaways</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(160, 160, 160);padding: 0px 30px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">🔝向上滑动阅览</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px);text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;overflow-y: auto;height: 198px;padding: 10px;width: 96%;border-radius: 7px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"text-align: justify;font-size: 14px;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 1px;padding: 0px 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\"></p>\n      <ol style=\"list-style-type: decimal;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 20px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n       <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">通用方法终将胜过为特定模型定制的复杂技巧</span></span></p>\n       </li>\n       <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">手工调优 Prompt 是一种典型的“过早优化”</span></p>\n       </li>\n       <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Prompt 是脆弱的抽象，它耦合了不该耦合的东西</span></p>\n       </li>\n       <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">回归工程基石：关注点分离</span></p>\n       </li>\n       <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">投资于“规约” (Specs)，而非易变的提示词</span></p>\n       </li>\n       <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">投资于“评估” (Evals)，它是检验价值的唯一标尺</span></p>\n       </li>\n       <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">投资于“代码”，用以实现可靠的控制流与工具</span></p>\n       </li>\n       <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">未来的框架，核心是解耦系统逻辑与底层工具</span></p>\n       </li>\n      </ol>\n      <p></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"padding-left:15px;margin-top:-18px;margin-bottom:-18px;box-sizing:border-box;padding-right:15px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">1</span></b></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">工程师的“沙塔”困境</span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"display: flex;width: 100%;flex-flow: column;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"z-index: 1;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"align-self:flex-start;padding:15px;box-shadow:rgb(231, 231, 231) 0px 0px 10px 0px;flex:0 0 auto;display:inline-block;width:98%;vertical-align:top;box-sizing:border-box;height:auto;\">\n       <div style=\"text-align: left;margin: 10px 0px 20px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=eec608a7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FBMIuxTte9jIOoNyOWSYBdU3ol4QlS7Zq8Xiah1pibF2TYQ0ycoTxWdeqZPH7S7oNR3cuR9p8z1RyZFjZmg3NwOBg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"text-align: justify;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(160, 160, 160);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><sub style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Omar Khattab</span></span></sub></strong><sub style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">: “我们正处在一个前所未有的时代，新的大语言模型（LLM）几乎每周都会发布，每一个都在质量、性能和成本之间提供了不同的权 new balance。”</span></span></sub></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><sub style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Omar Khattab</span></sub></strong><sub style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">: “Rich Sutton 的‘苦涩教训’指出，那些试图利用人类领域知识的复杂方法，最终往往不如那些受益于计算规模的通用方法，比如搜索和学习。”</span></sub></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"padding: 0px 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI 工程师正在经历一种前所未有的“沙塔”困境：</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们试图在不断流动的沙丘上，建造一座稳固的城堡</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">想象这个场景：你的团队花费数周，围绕一个特定模型精心打磨出一套近乎完美的 Prompt 体系，产品性能卓越。但转眼之间，业界发布了一款成本更低、能力更强的新模型。切换的命令下达，你却发现，过去积累的核心资产——那些精妙的提示词——在新模型面前几乎完全失效，系统性能一落千丈。于是，新一轮的“炼丹”开始了。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">2018 年，强化学习之父 Rich Sutton 提出了 AI 领域一条深刻的“苦涩教训”（The Bitter Lesson）。他发现，从长远看，那些试图将人类智慧硬编码进系统的“捷径”，总会被那些更简单、更通用、更能享受算力红利的方法所超越。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">DSPy 的作者 Omar Khattab 认为，这条教训对当下的 AI 工程极具现实意义。当然，工程的目标不是最大化通用智能，而是构建可靠、可控的系统。但这恰恰点明了问题的核心：我们是否过于依赖那些看似巧妙，实则脆弱的“人类知识”——比如，针对特定模型的 Prompt 技巧？</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"padding-left:15px;margin-top:-18px;margin-bottom:-18px;box-sizing:border-box;padding-right:15px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">2</span></b></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI 工程的“过早优化”</span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"display: flex;width: 100%;flex-flow: column;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"z-index: 1;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"align-self:flex-start;padding:15px;box-shadow:rgb(231, 231, 231) 0px 0px 10px 0px;flex:0 0 auto;display:inline-block;width:98%;vertical-align:top;box-sizing:border-box;height:auto;\">\n       <div style=\"text-align: left;margin: 10px 0px 20px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8b5a6dd9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FBMIuxTte9jIOoNyOWSYBdU3ol4QlS7ZqUcpcoru6qHL3jSu0RicA453arR49rDIbWXP20m0wB8O8BBr4NnkYPQA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"text-align: justify;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(160, 160, 160);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><sub style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Omar Khattab</span></span></sub></strong><sub style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">: “在低于合理抽象层次上对解决方案进行硬编码，就是 AI 工程中的‘过早优化’。”</span></span></sub><sub style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"></sub></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"padding: 0px 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">计算机科学史上，Donald Knuth 的名言“过早优化是万恶之源”影响了一代又一代的工程师。Omar 将这一经典原则，精准地指向了当下的 Prompt Engineering。他认为，当我们沉迷于为一个特定模型的特定行为“雕花”时，本质上就是在进行一种有害的“过早优化”。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">这好比为了实现开平方根的功能，你没有选择调用 math.sqrt() 这样的标准接口，而是直接深入到二进制层面去进行位操作。这种做法不仅复杂、易错，而且完全不具备可移植性。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">在 AI 应用中，我们的真实意图是“总结文本”或“提取信息”。但我们实际编写的 Prompt 却是：“请扮演一位资深分析师，以 Markdown 格式、分三点输出……” 这就是在错误的抽象层次上，用一堆脆弱的实现细节，去固化一个本该更通用的意图。</span></span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"padding-left:15px;margin-top:-18px;margin-bottom:-18px;box-sizing:border-box;padding-right:15px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">3</span></b></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">症结所在</span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">为什么 Prompt 是一种反工程的抽象？</span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"display: flex;width: 100%;flex-flow: column;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"z-index: 1;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"align-self:flex-start;padding:15px;box-shadow:rgb(231, 231, 231) 0px 0px 10px 0px;flex:0 0 auto;display:inline-block;width:98%;vertical-align:top;box-sizing:border-box;height:auto;\">\n       <div style=\"text-align: left;margin: 10px 0px 20px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3bade1a8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FBMIuxTte9jIOoNyOWSYBdU3ol4QlS7ZqYJpTgfystmEIF0C0NZ3j5T1RSWbfhHIJ9EQ1Wo1SqasyKpNAfdicBLg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"text-align: justify;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(160, 160, 160);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><sub style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Omar Khattab</span></span></sub></strong><sub style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">: “Prompt 是一个糟糕的编程抽象。它是一个‘字符串类型’的画布，将最基本的任务定义与那些针对特定模型的、半生不熟的决策紧密地耦合在了一起。”</span></span></sub></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"padding: 0px 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">这是 Omar 分享中最一针见血的论断。我们长期以来视为核心技能的提示词工程，其根基——Prompt 本身——就是一个极不稳定的编程抽象。</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">它的“糟糕”之处在于，它将多个本应彼此独立的关注点，强行“揉”在了一起。</span></strong></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">第一，它耦合了</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">任务定义与模型行为</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">。每一句提示词，都暗含着你对当前模型“脾气”的精妙洞察。一旦模型更新换代，这些洞察就可能变成一文不值的“屠龙之术”。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">第二，它耦合了</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">推理策略</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">。诸如“思维链”（Chain-of-Thought）这类本应属于高层策略的逻辑，被硬编码进了具体的提示文本中。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">第三，它耦合了</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">格式化与解析逻辑</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">。你不得不在 Prompt 里用自然语言小心翼翼地描述输出格式，再在代码里写一个同样脆弱的解析器来处理结果。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">那些“我会给你小费”或“你来扮演爱因斯坦”的技巧，在 Omar 看来，或许是有趣的“黑客行为”，但“绝非严肃的工程”。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"padding-left:15px;margin-top:-18px;margin-bottom:-18px;box-sizing:border-box;padding-right:15px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">4</span></b></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">回归基石：关注点分离</span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"display: flex;width: 100%;flex-flow: column;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"z-index: 1;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"align-self:flex-start;padding:15px;box-shadow:rgb(231, 231, 231) 0px 0px 10px 0px;flex:0 0 auto;display:inline-block;width:98%;vertical-align:top;box-sizing:border-box;height:auto;\">\n       <div style=\"text-align: left;margin: 10px 0px 20px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.2546296296296295\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=db5619e3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FBMIuxTte9jIOoNyOWSYBdU3ol4QlS7ZqENk5bnqkU633FZDyqdwyGBpec2ibkiaP4oPwcwEpnYsYGPuzBAHqn0Mg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"text-align: justify;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(160, 160, 160);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><sub style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Omar Khattab</span></span></sub></strong><sub style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">: “答案就是那个可靠的老朋友——关注点分离（Separation of Concerns）。”</span></span></sub></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"padding: 0px 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">既然症结在于不恰当的耦合，那么出路自然要回归软件工程的黄金法则：关注点分离。Omar 提出，AI 工程师应该将宝贵的精力，投资在三类更稳定、更具长期价值的资产上：</span></p>\n    <ol style=\"list-style-type: decimal;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 20px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">自然语言规约 (Specs):</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;这是对任务最本质的描述，定义了“做什么”，而非“怎么做”。例如，“判断用户评论的情感倾向”。它是系统的意图核心，不应随模型变化而变化。</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">评估 (Evals):</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;这是系统的验收标准与行为准则。一套高质量的评估数据集和标准，是定义系统正确性的“锚”。无论底层技术如何变迁，评估体系是衡量商业价值唯一可靠的标尺。</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">代码 (Code):</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;用代码处理所有要求确定性和可靠性的事务。包括定义工具接口、管理数据隐私、实现复杂的业务逻辑。这些是 LLM 尚无法可靠处理的领域，也是工程师价值的集中体现。</span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ol>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">一个设计优良的 AI 系统，应该能让这三者松散耦合，从而实现对底层模型的“热插拔”。</span></strong></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"padding-left:15px;margin-top:-18px;margin-bottom:-18px;box-sizing:border-box;padding-right:15px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">5</span></b></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">投资于“不变”，驾驭“万变”</span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"display: flex;width: 100%;flex-flow: column;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"z-index: 1;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"align-self:flex-start;padding:15px;box-shadow:rgb(231, 231, 231) 0px 0px 10px 0px;flex:0 0 auto;display:inline-block;width:98%;vertical-align:top;box-sizing:border-box;height:auto;\">\n       <div style=\"text-align: left;margin: 10px 0px 20px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e32e097e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FBMIuxTte9jIOoNyOWSYBdU3ol4QlS7ZqURHjXkwf7TAYM8o7LPy3LNK25KEYeljZUtNpSB1VC6gUoiaHHIVDfzA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"text-align: justify;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(160, 160, 160);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><sub style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Omar Khattab</span></span></sub></strong><sub style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">: “要避免在低于当前必要的抽象层次上手动进行工程。安全的投资包括：定义签名、核心的控制流和工具、以及全面的评估。”</span></span></sub><sub style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"></sub></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"padding: 0px 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Omar 的分享，为所有在技术浪潮中感到焦虑的工程师，指明了一条清晰的价值投资之路。我们应该停止追逐那些转瞬即逝的技巧，回归工程本质，投资于那些能够穿越周期的资产：</span></p>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 20px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-2\">\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">投资于“签名”：</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">定义清晰的模块规约。</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">投资于“工具与流程”：</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">构建可靠、可复用的代码资产。</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">投资于“评估”：</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">建立自动化的评估体系，作为系统迭代的北极星。</span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">如此，我们便能将系统的核心逻辑，锚定在更高、更稳固的抽象层上。底层的模型和算法可以随时更迭，但我们构建的系统价值却得以沉淀和累积。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"padding-left:15px;margin-top:-18px;margin-bottom:-18px;box-sizing:border-box;padding-right:15px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">6</span></b></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">两种工程师，两种命运</span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">（此节为根据演讲精神演绎的故事）</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"display: flex;width: 100%;flex-flow: column;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"z-index: 1;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"align-self:flex-start;padding:15px;box-shadow:rgb(231, 231, 231) 0px 0px 10px 0px;flex:0 0 auto;display:inline-block;width:98%;vertical-align:top;box-sizing:border-box;height:auto;\">\n       <div style=\"text-align: left;margin: 10px 0px 20px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5055555555555555\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4e185331&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FBMIuxTte9jIOoNyOWSYBdU3ol4QlS7ZqBicnF4P3qWBr3NzSB38QPOq4NIiaHQN8fPxeRNqzLZ34BZgJuJjR6omg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"padding: 0px 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">小王和小李接到同一个任务：构建一个企业内部的 RAG 知识问答系统。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">小王是一位顶尖的“提示词炼金术士”。他耗费心血，写出了一段包含上千单词的“究极 Prompt”，对上下文组织、回答风格、输出格式的控制都达到了像素级。系统上线后，基于 GPT-4 表现惊艳。然而，当公司决定切换到另一款性价比更高的新模型时，这套 Prompt 立刻失灵，小王不得不推倒重来，他的核心竞争力在一夜之间被“版本更新”清零了。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">小李则是一位“系统架构师”。他首先将任务分解为Retrieve和Synthesize两个核心模块，并为它们定义了清晰的输入输出签名。他没有手写任何具体的 Prompt，而是将主要精力放在了准备高质量的评估数据集上。当需要更换模型时，他只修改了一行配置，然后让 DSPy 的优化器自动为新模型寻找最佳实现。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">在这个故事里，小王的价值与特定的“炼丹炉”（模型）深度绑定。而小李的价值，则体现在他所设计的、能够适应任何“炼丹炉”的、稳健的系统架构之上。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"padding:0px 15px;letter-spacing:2px;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 27px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">结语</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 12px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Closing Thoughts</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"padding: 0px 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">在 AI 工程的草莽时代，我们很容易将“奇技淫巧”误认为核心竞争力，将“术”的精通等同于“道”的掌握。Omar Khattab 的分享如同一声警钟，它呼唤我们跳出“手写 Prompt”的战术泥潭，回归到“构建稳健系统”的战略高度。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">从依赖“炼金术”和个人英雄主义，到建立依赖架构和自动化流程的“现代工业体系”，这不仅是一个技术选择，更是一个行业走向成熟的必经之路。</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">投资于评估、规约和代码，而非易碎的提示词</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">，才能让我们不再吃“苦涩的教训”，拥抱 AI 进步的红利。</span></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章批判 AI 工程中过度依赖 Prompt 调优的脆弱性，提倡回归软件工程原则，投资于规约、评估与代码，构建可插拔的稳健系统。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章批判 AI 工程中过度依赖 Prompt 调优的脆弱性，提倡回归软件工程原则，投资于规约、评估与代码，构建可插拔的稳健系统。",
  "summary": "文章深度分析了当前 AI 工程领域中过度依赖“提示词炼金术”的弊端。作者引用 DSPy 作者 Omar Khattab 的观点，指出手动调优 Prompt 是一种“过早优化”，它将任务定义、模型行为、推理策略和格式化逻辑紧密耦合，导致系统脆弱且难以维护。这种做法使得 AI 系统像“沙塔”一样，一旦底层 LLM 模型更新，前期投入的 Prompt 资产便可能失效。文章呼吁 AI 工程师回归软件工程的“关注点分离”原则，将精力投入到更具长期价值的“规约 (Specs)”、“评估 (Evals)”和“代码 (Code)”上。规约定义任务本质，评估作为系统验收标准，代码则处理确定性逻辑和工具集成。通过这种方式，实现系统核心逻辑与底层模型的解耦，使得模型可以“热插拔”，从而构建出稳健、可扩展且不过时的 AI 工程系统。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "手动调优 Prompt 是 AI 工程中的“过早优化”和脆弱抽象",
      "explanation": "Prompt 将任务定义、模型行为、推理策略和格式化逻辑强行耦合，导致系统对底层模型变化高度敏感，维护成本高且难以移植。"
    },
    {
      "point": "应当回归软件工程的“关注点分离”原则，解耦 AI 系统",
      "explanation": "将系统意图（规约）、验收标准（评估）和确定性逻辑（代码）分离，实现底层模型的“热插拔”，提升系统稳健性。"
    },
    {
      "point": "投资于“规约、评估和代码”是构建不过时 AI 工程的关键",
      "explanation": "规约定义任务本质，评估提供可靠衡量标准，代码处理稳定逻辑，这些是长期积累和复利的资产，而非转瞬即逝的 Prompt 技巧。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "不要痴迷于调提示词，要把时间精力投资在更稳定有复利的事儿上。",
    "我们试图在不断流动的沙丘上，建造一座稳固的城堡。",
    "Prompt 是一个糟糕的编程抽象。它是一个'字符串类型'的画布，将最基本的任务定义与那些针对特定模型的、半生不熟的决策紧密地耦合在了一起。",
    "答案就是那个可靠的老朋友------关注点分离（Separation of Concerns）。",
    "投资于评估、规约和代码，而非易碎的提示词，才能让我们不再吃'苦涩的教训'，拥抱 AI 进步的红利。"
  ],
